snippet.title: Time Clickers Teaser Trailer
snippet.description:
Time Clickers
http://timegamers.com/

Google Play Store
https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.ProtonStudio.TimeClickers

Apple App Store
https://itunes.apple.com/us/app/time-clickers/id1008083724?mt=8

Steam
http://store.steampowered.com/app/385770

Your mission starts now!  Collect gold, upgrade your Click Pistol & hire a team of elite sharp-shooters to help with defeating the enemies in this Free clicker idle game.
